wdi2-SP.POP.1564.TO.ZS.def: Total population between the ages 15 to 64 as a percentage of the total population. Population is based on the de facto definition of population, which counts all residents regardless of legal status or citizenship.
wdi2-SP.POP.1564.TO.ZS.name: Population ages 15-64
wdi2-SP.POP.1564.TO.ZS.source: United Nations Population Division. World Population Prospects: 2022 Revision.
